  "message": "chore(config): replace hardcoded bearer token with testtoken and narrow MCP log filter\n\nMCP config files:\n- Replace the hardcoded SHA-256 bearer token in codex.mcp.json,\n  cursor.mcp.json, and gemini.mcp.json with \"testtoken\" to avoid\n  committing production secrets to the repository.\n\nmain.rs:\n- Narrow default_mcp_log_filter() from global \"info\" to \"warn\" with\n  explicit \"info\" for the 6 mcp_agent_mail_* crates, matching the\n  same change applied to default_release_log_filter() in the CLI\n  crate. This reduces noise from third-party dependencies (especially\n  fsqlite internals) in MCP/stdio mode.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>",
